FBIS4-12593 "drnes069_l_94014" FBIS-NES-94-069 Daily Report 6 Apr 1994 ISRAEL Five IDF Soldiers Lightly Wounded in Gaza Five IDF Soldiers Lightly Wounded in Gaza TA0604182794 Jerusalem Israel Television Channel 1 Network in Hebrew 1700 GMT 6 Apr 94 TA0604182794 Jerusalem Israel Television Channel 1 Network in Hebrew 1700 GMT 6 Apr 94 Hebrew BFN [Text] Five IDF [Israel Defense Forces] soldiers were lightly injured in Gaza this evening by a hand grenade thrown at a jeep in which they were riding. Our correspondent Alon Ben-David reports that the five were on patrol on al-Nasir Street in Gaza. The IDF is conducting searches for the perpetrators.
